No. 09-10281 (09A980). Darryl Durr, Petitioner v. Richard Cordray, Attorney General of Ohio, et al. 559 U.S. 1087, 130 S. Ct. 2147,

176 L. Ed. 2d 757,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 3477. April 19, 2010.

Application for stay of execution of sentence of death, presented to Justice Stevens, and by him referred to the Court, denied. Petition for writ of *758certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit denied.

Same case below, 602 F.3d 731.
